Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.93,0:00:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,居住在精靈球裡的寵物 簡稱寵物小精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.17,0:00:28.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這星球上非常不可思議的生物
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.98,0:00:33.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們的種類有 一百 兩百 三百…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.98,0:00:36.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 也許會比這更多
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:43.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精靈與人類作為朋友與夥伴齊心協力
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.15,0:00:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但有時也會作為敵人而對立
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:49.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它們居於在世界的各處
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.95,0:00:55.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,接下來這位少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真新鎮的小智
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.95,0:01:01.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為小精靈大師
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.48,0:01:02.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不斷對戰與收服
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,持續著自己的修行之旅
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.27,0:01:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與小精靈的相遇
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.75,0:01:12.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與小精靈的離別
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.72,0:01:17.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就此 無數的故事相繼而生
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.79,0:01:25.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 那是從很遙遠 很遙遠的過去開始的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.86,0:01:41.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(300,800)}『很久以前…還沒有小精靈球的時代…』
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.66,0:02:27.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導之力 存於我心
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.94,0:03:43.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.43,0:03:45.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.97,0:04:01.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.67,0:04:04.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽到了 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.77,0:04:06.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數量龐大的軍隊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.47,0:04:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,讓它們交手的話
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.80,0:04:10.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一人無能為力
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.26,0:04:12.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣下去的話…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.79,0:04:19.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭真的已經不可避免了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.99,0:05:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能離開這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.57,0:05:03.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是這裡的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.36,0:05:05.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的命運與這城堡是連在一起的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.06,0:05:06.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.66,0:06:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.79,0:06:12.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.80,0:06:13.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的眼睛
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.04,0:06:15.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我沒事
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.02,0:06:18.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,離開這個地方
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.35,0:06:21.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我已經拋棄了那座城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.34,0:06:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就不會再回到那裡去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您是什麼意思
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.62,0:06:30.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.79,0:06:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.09,0:06:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為…什麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.21,0:07:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,樹…創世之樹…正在哭泣著…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.09,0:08:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.03,0:09:30.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳女王明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.13,0:09:32.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是波導使者亞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.17,0:09:38.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,與夢幻讓創世之樹發出它的力量
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.94,0:09:39.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,然後呢
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.63,0:09:42.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,戰爭停止了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.33,0:09:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,憎恨與憤怒也平靜下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.62,0:09:49.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精靈們也回到了自己生活地方去了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.22,0:09:55.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,於是這片大地也恢復了和平
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.74,0:09:57.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.22,0:10:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因此亞倫就被人們稱為「波導的勇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.12,0:10:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下次再給我講哦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.13,0:10:09.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導的勇者的故事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.94,0:10:11.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.26,0:10:16.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,800)}『然後 現在…』
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.96,0:11:47.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了成為小精靈大師
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.74,0:11:49.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,而持續旅行的小智一行人
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.71,0:11:52.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,來到了這座奧爾多蘭城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.81,0:11:58.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為了參加讚頌波導的勇者亞倫而舉行的祭典
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.13,0:12:01.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在城內的小精靈對戰中獲勝的人
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.70,0:12:05.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,將會被尊為今年的「波導的勇者」
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.22,0:12:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,服裝的話 不穿上古代的衣服是不能參加的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.31,0:12:14.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 沒帶這種衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.93,0:12:17.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城裡已經準備好衣服了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.04,0:12:18.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.91,0:12:20.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許還有勇者的衣服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.90,0:12:24.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的話也要把皮卡丘打扮起來
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.37,0:12:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許會很不錯哦
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.86,0:12:59.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以在這裡面選嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.89,0:13:02.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪件比較好呢 眼花繚亂啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.47,0:13:03.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的服裝在哪裡呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.29,0:13:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的話…呃…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.57,0:13:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.38,0:13:36.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.04,0:13:38.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,正是在下
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.51,0:13:40.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 很合適呢
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.57,0:13:41.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.33,0:13:43.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是勇者了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.77,0:13:44.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼樣 皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.69,0:13:58.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可愛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.20,0:13:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很適合哦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.34,0:14:02.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精靈對戰差不多要開始了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 皮卡丘 走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.68,0:14:15.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,趁大家樂此不疲的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.56,0:14:18.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把這個城堡的小精靈都抓走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.88,0:14:19.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,噢～
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.95,0:14:21.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,首先 要換身衣服呢
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.82,0:14:23.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要打扮成什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.67,0:14:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快一點啦
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.98,0:14:27.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個超棒耶 啊哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.53,0:14:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好…好快
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.56,0:14:43.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個國家的女王
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.84,0:14:46.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾多蘭城的城主
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.57,0:14:48.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,艾琳殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:15:00.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下 真是漂亮啊
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.26,0:15:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在為讚頌拯救世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.04,0:15:06.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導的勇者——亞倫舉行的小精靈對戰開始
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.10,0:15:25.24,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,光　大地立
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.07,0:15:31.30,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠　誓
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.97,0:15:37.27,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,笑顏　淚
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.90,0:15:43.33,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,　忘
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.02,0:15:49.26,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,想　距離飛越
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.96,0:15:58.06,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,今　君屆　
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.31,0:15:59.23,oped,NTP,0,0,0,,！！
