Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.00,0:16:47.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,(2006)時間軸：ssaassaa
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.00,0:16:52.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,(2006)特效：EDL
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.00,0:16:57.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,(2012)校對：superbabyXP {\fsp-7}Ｇａm{\r}ver
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.00,0:17:02.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,(2012)後期：MR
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.00,0:17:07.00,staff,NTP,0,0,0,,為愛而做 請勿用於商業用途
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.38,0:17:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瑪狃拉無法戰鬥 皮卡丘獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.64,0:17:27.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以今年波導的勇者是
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.70,0:17:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真新鎮的小智
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.83,0:17:32.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,耶～太棒了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.57,0:17:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.72,0:17:49.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你和皮卡丘 真是最好的搭檔呢
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.99,0:17:51.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.09,0:17:57.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是琪朵 請多多指教
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.17,0:17:57.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小智
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.59,0:18:00.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下是小剛
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.03,0:18:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下非常渴望成為漂亮的大姐姐最好的夥伴…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.04,0:18:05.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好啦好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.24,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊啊好痛好痛好痛…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.61,0:18:08.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,同伴到那邊去找好啦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.01,0:18:35.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是波導的勇者亞倫曾經持有的勇者之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.32,0:18:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只有在祭典的對戰中獲勝 被選為勇者的人才能擁有
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.00,0:18:45.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.61,0:18:48.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請接受它吧 小智
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.23,0:18:48.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.45,0:18:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是波導的勇者之杖
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.49,0:19:00.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.80,0:19:04.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您說什麼了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.43,0:19:06.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.71,0:19:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為讚頌保護這個國家和平的勇者亞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.76,0:19:15.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今晚就快樂地慶祝吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.41,0:19:38.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪…琪朵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.27,0:19:41.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可…可以和我一起跳…跳支舞嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.37,0:19:42.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.72,0:19:44.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,榮幸之至
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.21,0:19:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用那麼緊張啊
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:51.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會帶你的
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.44,0:19:52.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.70,0:20:08.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.52,0:20:12.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 大家也一起來享受宴會的快樂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.99,0:20:23.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請允許我失陪一下
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:27.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家出來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.32,0:20:36.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 我也要去飽餐一頓了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.41,0:20:42.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您不能去 勇者大人是不能離席的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.31,0:20:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.99,0:21:07.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在不是捕捉小精靈的機會嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.48,0:21:09.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多跳一會兒啦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.49,0:21:11.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難得穿上這麼漂亮的禮服
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.71,0:21:11.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.99,0:21:15.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,您跳得真棒
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.91,0:21:17.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.37,0:21:20.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,男人…戀愛的預感…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.84,0:21:23.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.03,0:21:27.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們是不是在哪裡見過
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.65,0:21:30.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不不 沒有的事
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.28,0:21:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣的盛宴真是食慾大開啊
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.72,0:21:54.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小剛 能拿點喝的來嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.70,0:21:56.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然可以 請等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:22:16.08,0:22:17.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你那裡已經是早上了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:18.54,0:22:20.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,早飯吃什麼了 班克斯
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,牛角麵包和咖啡
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.50,0:22:25.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃點沙拉比較好
Dialogue: 0,0:22:25.43,0:22:28.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就再來點蔬菜汁吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.82,0:22:29.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,芹菜也要放進去哦
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.42,0:22:32.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個不喜歡吃
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.40,0:22:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以挑食啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.95,0:22:35.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那今天就吃一次吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.34,0:22:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小姐那裡的晚宴怎麼樣呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.68,0:22:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,城堡的舞會是不是很豐盛啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.61,0:22:46.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,稍微吃了點 工作完成後再吃了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.00,0:22:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是可憐你了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.15,0:22:49.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經習慣了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.78,0:22:52.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,話說回來 請把這座城堡的地圖傳送過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.87,0:22:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等我沖涼之後給你傳送可以麼
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.22,0:22:55.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.20,0:22:58.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我可是還餓著呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.60,0:23:00.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼請再等30秒左右
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.14,0:23:02.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,20秒
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.23,0:23:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.06,0:23:09.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,久等了 傳送開始
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.36,0:23:11.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.58,0:23:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請不要勉強自己哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.85,0:23:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是是 我知道了 執行長班克斯大人
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.00,0:23:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定是我們的競爭對手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.77,0:23:41.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘它們到哪去了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.62,0:23:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛比獸
Dialogue: 0,0:25:11.82,0:25:14.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請問…請問…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.80,0:25:16.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.84,0:25:19.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好興奮…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.50,0:25:50.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.90,0:26:28.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找到你咯
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.96,0:26:32.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,聽著 把這個發信器放到夢幻身上
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.23,0:26:50.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.54,0:27:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,做得太過頭了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:27:32.35,0:27:34.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只是安置發信器而已
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.65,0:27:41.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.65,0:27:47.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒用的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:28:12.30,0:28:14.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對付我們綽綽有餘啊
Dialogue: 0,0:28:24.25,0:28:26.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 皮卡丘 和喵喵
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.02,0:28:30.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.90,0:28:38.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瞬間…移動
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.76,0:28:52.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒想到皮卡丘那麼重
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.59,0:29:09.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩人一起上的話應該能馬上完成的
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.56,0:29:22.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.88,0:29:37.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是幾百年前的人持有的嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.23,0:29:39.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可思議的感覺
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.33,0:29:45.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:29:46.77,0:29:47.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,又聽到了
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.19,0:29:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在 即將拉開今晚宴會的帷幕
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.71,0:29:57.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,由波導的勇者向大家展示絕技
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.69,0:30:00.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快 勇者的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:00.68,0:30:02.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,勇者的造型
Dialogue: 0,0:30:20.92,0:30:22.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:30:25.58,0:30:26.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.88,0:30:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,裡面有什麼東西
Dialogue: 0,0:30:55.95,0:30:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.86,0:31:02.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼要丟下城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:31:03.31,0:31:04.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心靈感應
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.97,0:31:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:05.89,0:31:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.66,0:31:22.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是
Dialogue: 0,0:31:22.89,0:31:23.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.23,0:31:25.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:31:25.44,0:31:28.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,追隨勇者亞倫的小精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.22,0:31:29.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的
Dialogue: 0,0:31:29.60,0:31:30.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這裡面
Dialogue: 0,0:31:43.73,0:31:45.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是奧爾多蘭城嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.28,0:32:01.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:32:02.41,0:32:05.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,今天開始 這裡就是你我一起生活的城堡了
Dialogue: 0,0:32:05.86,0:32:07.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,修行會很嚴厲的
Dialogue: 0,0:32:07.42,0:32:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.47,0:32:09.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,作為波導使者
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.63,0:32:12.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我會把我全部的技能教給你
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.12,0:32:14.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:32:14.74,0:32:15.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導之力存於我心
Dialogue: 0,0:32:19.22,0:32:21.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,相信自己的波導之力
Dialogue: 0,0:32:55.93,0:32:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.02,0:33:00.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:33:02.13,0:33:03.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不是琳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.74,0:33:08.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琳女王是我的先祖
Dialogue: 0,0:33:09.33,0:33:11.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的名字是艾琳
Dialogue: 0,0:33:18.94,0:33:21.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你一直在沉睡喲
Dialogue: 0,0:33:22.03,0:33:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沉睡
Dialogue: 0,0:33:23.48,0:33:25.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時光已經流逝
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.47,0:33:27.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼會
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.51,0:33:31.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,昨天這裡…還是我們的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:33:32.16,0:33:35.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或許對於你來說只是昨天的事情
Dialogue: 0,0:33:35.65,0:33:38.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對我們來說已經是很久遠了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:44.90,0:33:48.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說你在戰鬥中下落不明
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.40,0:33:51.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底發生什麼事了
Dialogue: 0,0:33:51.96,0:33:53.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,兩股軍隊正要開戰
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.30,0:33:56.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座城堡即將被捲入紛爭
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.51,0:33:59.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我被派去執行偵查
Dialogue: 0,0:33:59.96,0:34:02.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是已經無法找到
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.26,0:34:03.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,阻止戰爭的方法了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:03.95,0:34:06.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是勇者亞倫不是阻止了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:06.53,0:34:07.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:34:07.37,0:34:11.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據傳說是亞倫拯救了城堡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:11.71,0:34:12.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.03,0:34:13.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:34:14.99,0:34:15.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.34,0:34:17.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拋棄了城堡逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.96,0:34:19.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還將我封印了起來
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.99,0:34:21.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像和傳說不太一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.77,0:34:22.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼回事呢
Dialogue: 0,0:34:28.76,0:34:32.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,現在已經無法知道事情的真相了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.70,0:34:35.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我到底…怎麼了…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:35.56,0:34:36.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.65,0:34:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在你的心緒平和之前 就留在這裡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.47,0:34:43.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,奧爾蘭多城堡歡迎你
Dialogue: 0,0:34:45.02,0:34:47.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,女王殿下 感激不盡
Dialogue: 0,0:34:47.95,0:34:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我叫小智
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.22,0:34:50.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你把我和誰搞錯了
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.85,0:34:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.96,0:34:55.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 是因為這個服裝的原因吧
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.77,0:34:56.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.62,0:34:59.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的波導和亞倫大人是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:35:00.81,0:35:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那隻小精靈從來都沒看到過耶 不是嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.17,0:35:07.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因為那是被封印了好幾百年的小精靈吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.69,0:35:09.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要 好想得到它
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.94,0:35:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不好了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.11,0:35:12.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.03,0:35:13.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:14.16,0:35:16.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻 我看到夢幻了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:16.97,0:35:20.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 能看到夢幻 真是個好運的男孩
Dialogue: 0,0:35:20.43,0:35:23.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,據說看到夢幻的是能夠帶來幸福的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.95,0:35:25.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是啦
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.27,0:35:26.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,到底怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.69,0:35:29.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻和皮卡丘還有喵喵一起消失了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:30.96,0:35:31.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.47,0:35:34.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小精靈
Dialogue: 0,0:35:34.69,0:35:38.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它是被勇者亞倫封印在杖裡面的小精靈 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.96,0:35:40.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才復甦了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:40.27,0:35:41.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:41.68,0:35:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你真的看到夢幻了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.51,0:35:44.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不會搞錯了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.01,0:35:46.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也看到了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.78,0:35:49.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從瞭望塔那裡帶著皮卡丘和喵喵的夢幻
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.75,0:35:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,變成比雕飛走了
Dialogue: 0,0:35:52.54,0:35:54.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼夢幻要做這種事
Dialogue: 0,0:35:54.71,0:35:56.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大概是惡作劇吧
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.15,0:36:00.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在這個城堡裡 夢幻會時不時地出現 搞些惡作劇
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.74,0:36:04.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,經常會少些玩具什麼的 之後從來沒再出現過
Dialogue: 0,0:36:05.14,0:36:06.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,連喵喵也一起被帶走了
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.31,0:36:10.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也就是說本來想抓小精靈的 卻反而被抓走了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.82,0:36:13.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 不是這個問題…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.38,0:36:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,請告訴我夢幻在什麼地方
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.29,0:36:17.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我要去找皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.08,0:36:37.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看見那棵巨大的樹了嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.71,0:36:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實是巨大的岩石山峰
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.27,0:36:42.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壯觀
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.96,0:36:46.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們把它叫做「創世之樹」
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.42,0:36:49.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創世之樹
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.52,0:36:51.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻就住在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:36:52.75,0:36:53.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.35,0:36:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:36:55.22,0:36:58.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻可以變成各種各樣小精靈的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:36:58.62,0:37:02.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎不會在人們面前展現出本來的樣子
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.89,0:37:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 該怎麼找到它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.92,0:37:08.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐 可以看出各種各樣的波導
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.18,0:37:12.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說就算在暗夜之中也可以為勇者指路
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.87,0:37:16.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐 你應該能夠找到夢幻吧
Dialogue: 0,0:37:16.68,0:37:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:18.00,0:37:20.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你願意把你的力量借助給小智嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.69,0:37:23.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全憑女王殿下吩咐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.50,0:37:25.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:37:26.48,0:37:28.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也會出力的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:28.51,0:37:29.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,琪朵小姐
Dialogue: 0,0:37:29.73,0:37:33.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 你是那個冒險家琪朵·夏瑪茲
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.56,0:37:35.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.03,0:37:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你就在我的身邊 我居然沒有發覺
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.72,0:37:40.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我真該好好地
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.29,0:37:42.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,深深地自我反省啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.32,0:37:45.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能見到你真是感動萬分啊
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.78,0:37:46.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她很有名嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.96,0:37:48.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那當然啦
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.10,0:37:53.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在我這本排名手冊中可是有明確紀錄的
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.86,0:37:57.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,熱氣球繞世界一周的最短紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.00,0:38:01.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單人潛水艇海底探測的最深紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.62,0:38:04.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,單獨宇宙漫步的最長紀錄 等等
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:07.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,擁有好多世界紀錄
Dialogue: 0,0:38:07.51,0:38:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是女強人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:10.61,0:38:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厲害啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.96,0:38:14.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能和這樣的人一起前往就可以放心了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.11,0:38:16.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.63,0:38:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.49,0:38:25.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實 我來這個城鎮的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.15,0:38:29.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是為了揭開創世之樹的秘密
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.48,0:38:31.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.73,0:38:33.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算你們不拜託 我也會一起去的
Dialogue: 0,0:38:33.93,0:38:34.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.92,0:38:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 明天早上出發吧
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.16,0:38:41.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘也許現在正和夢幻一起玩呢
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.66,0:38:43.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果真是那樣就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.76,0:39:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你幹什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.12,0:39:18.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,誰叫你一聲不響走在我的身後
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.18,0:39:21.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明天就拜託你了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.40,0:39:24.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我一定要找到皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:39:24.66,0:39:26.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是那只皮卡丘的主人嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:39:27.44,0:39:28.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,主人
Dialogue: 0,0:39:29.35,0:39:30.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是那樣啦
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.85,0:39:32.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我和皮卡丘是朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.44,0:39:34.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友
Dialogue: 0,0:39:35.65,0:39:37.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,朋友不見了
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.18,0:39:39.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然要去找吧 你也是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:39:39.93,0:39:42.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我這麼做只是為了女王殿下
Dialogue: 0,0:39:47.34,0:39:48.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛 那個傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.99,0:40:25.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導之力 請保護他們吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:40.04,0:40:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺就像在雲裡啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.55,0:40:44.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐它沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.17,0:40:46.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它擁有波導之力
Dialogue: 0,0:40:46.96,0:40:47.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.05,0:40:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐曾說過
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.30,0:40:53.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智的波導和亞倫的波導是相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:53.52,0:40:56.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對了 波導到底是什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:40:56.48,0:40:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一切事物都是有波導的
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.63,0:41:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼 我們也有波導
Dialogue: 0,0:41:02.13,0:41:04.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,類似於氣息或者光環的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:05.02,0:41:07.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那就是魯卡利歐看到的東西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.72,0:41:09.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的 在傳說的時代中
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.14,0:41:12.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有著可以操縱波導的人
Dialogue: 0,0:41:12.27,0:41:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被稱為波導使者
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.79,0:41:16.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫就是其中之一
Dialogue: 0,0:41:25.07,0:41:28.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,如果說那個亞倫和小智的波導相同的話
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.63,0:41:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼小智也可以操縱波導
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.96,0:41:31.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:33.23,0:41:34.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好痛
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.80,0:41:35.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好像不行啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.97,0:41:36.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,確實呢
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.26,0:42:17.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.69,0:42:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還沒有醒啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:37.13,0:42:38.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好了 完成了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.95,0:42:40.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給小智的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.30,0:42:41.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:41.05,0:42:42.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給小正的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:42.64,0:42:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:43.01,0:42:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給小遙的
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.30,0:42:44.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.73,0:42:46.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是給琪朵小…奇怪
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.79,0:42:50.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 這是什麼小精靈啊
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.66,0:42:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 那可是給琪朵小姐的耶
Dialogue: 0,0:42:57.30,0:42:58.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 把它弄哭了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:58.88,0:43:00.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼可以欺負人家呢
Dialogue: 0,0:43:00.52,0:43:02.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是胡說盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:43:02.47,0:43:04.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很擅長騙人哦
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.32,0:43:07.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.06,0:43:15.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不可以拿別人的東西
Dialogue: 0,0:43:15.96,0:43:16.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,吃這個吧
Dialogue: 0,0:44:25.71,0:44:27.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感覺真是棒呢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:18.78,0:45:20.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.95,0:45:42.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好壯觀啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:20.77,0:46:21.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,間歇泉啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.42,0:46:24.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在結束之間 只能等了
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.24,0:46:28.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.51,0:46:29.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,溫泉
Dialogue: 0,0:46:36.97,0:46:38.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 舒服啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:46.31,0:46:48.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也跟過來了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.55,0:46:51.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也一起過去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:46:54.18,0:46:55.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡說盆栽
Dialogue: 0,0:46:58.65,0:47:01.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,胡說盆栽是岩石系的 所以它不喜歡水啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.00,0:47:02.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:07.08,0:47:10.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘要是也能來這裡泡溫泉就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:11.18,0:47:12.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它一定會很開心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:47:13.21,0:47:13.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:28.43,0:47:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:47:29.48,0:47:31.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也把腳伸到這裡面來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:31.34,0:47:32.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:32.62,0:47:34.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不用了
Dialogue: 0,0:47:34.76,0:47:35.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不要拘束啦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.99,0:47:37.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那麼
Dialogue: 0,0:47:44.07,0:47:44.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:45.42,0:47:45.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:47:51.87,0:47:52.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:47:54.14,0:47:55.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:47:55.45,0:47:56.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:47:56.61,0:47:58.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很舒服的喲～
Dialogue: 0,0:48:07.89,0:48:09.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:09.53,0:48:11.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能不喜歡溫泉吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.60,0:48:13.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智 過來下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.06,0:48:15.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了 小遙
Dialogue: 0,0:48:16.77,0:48:17.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那邊
Dialogue: 0,0:48:19.14,0:48:20.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那個是…花
Dialogue: 0,0:48:21.16,0:48:22.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我去看看
Dialogue: 0,0:48:25.49,0:48:26.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智還真靈活
Dialogue: 0,0:48:27.34,0:48:28.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看起來像長尾怪手呢
Dialogue: 0,0:48:48.08,0:48:50.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可不能亂采山上的花啊 小智
Dialogue: 0,0:48:50.82,0:48:52.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊 對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:48:52.52,0:48:53.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真沒辦法
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.92,0:48:56.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下再種下吧
Dialogue: 0,0:48:56.91,0:48:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:03.78,0:49:05.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是時間之花
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.30,0:49:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間之花
Dialogue: 0,0:49:06.70,0:49:11.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這種花可以讓波導使者看見時間的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:49:30.63,0:49:31.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這樣可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:32.33,0:49:33.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.08,0:49:35.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小遙 給我吧
Dialogue: 0,0:49:35.35,0:49:35.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.90,0:49:41.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.01,0:49:59.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,剛才那是
Dialogue: 0,0:50:00.62,0:50:01.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是時間之花
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.15,0:50:03.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間之花
Dialogue: 0,0:50:03.88,0:50:04.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,傳說中
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.12,0:50:08.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,波導使者可以通過這個看見時間的奇跡
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.12,0:50:10.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是指這個呢
Dialogue: 0,0:50:10.78,0:50:12.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是不可思議啊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:12.29,0:50:15.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一定是因為小智和亞倫擁有相同的波導
Dialogue: 0,0:50:15.78,0:50:16.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,才發生奇跡了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:21.83,0:50:24.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘最初和我在一起的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.98,0:50:26.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,和現在是不一樣的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.79,0:50:27.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是這樣嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.62,0:50:30.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一點都不友好
Dialogue: 0,0:50:30.72,0:50:32.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被它電了不知道多少次了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.21,0:50:34.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼成為好朋友的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.92,0:50:35.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.06,0:50:40.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也想知道小智和皮卡丘是怎樣才變得這麼要好的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:41.21,0:50:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,開始旅途的那天
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.82,0:50:44.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,被烈雀襲擊
Dialogue: 0,0:50:45.81,0:50:47.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之後通過兩人的努力才度過難關的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.04,0:50:50.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這就是成為朋友的契機吧
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.38,0:51:06.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,原來是這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:51:07.33,0:51:10.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那以後 皮卡丘開始信任我
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.71,0:51:12.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也開始信任皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:51:22.93,0:51:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也可以的
Dialogue: 0,0:51:25.43,0:51:27.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我相信你 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:51:45.66,0:51:47.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 就到這
Dialogue: 0,0:52:03.36,0:52:04.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有什麼好信任的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.00,0:52:07.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,人類是靠不住的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:09.10,0:52:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:52:12.86,0:52:14.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你是說我嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:14.40,0:52:16.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你要是遇到了什麼困境
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.33,0:52:17.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說不定也會把皮卡丘給拋棄了
Dialogue: 0,0:52:18.07,0:52:20.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我是絕對不會拋棄皮卡丘的
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.94,0:52:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這誰知道呢
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.87,0:52:27.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,歷代相傳為勇者的人
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.18,0:52:31.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,會這麼簡單就將自己的小精靈拋棄嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.26,0:52:33.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只不過是你在胡說八道吧
Dialogue: 0,0:52:34.02,0:52:34.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:52:35.38,0:52:36.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別這樣啊
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.88,0:52:38.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是這傢伙
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.19,0:52:39.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:52:39.89,0:52:44.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就是因為你這愚蠢的主人而逃跑的也說不定
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.18,0:52:46.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.62,0:52:53.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:52:53.75,0:52:54.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手
Dialogue: 0,0:53:05.40,0:53:06.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別打架啊
Dialogue: 0,0:53:17.88,0:53:20.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們自己人開始吵起來了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:20.59,0:53:22.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比起這個來 我的肚子已經餓了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.16,0:53:23.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,去找點什…
Dialogue: 0,0:53:23.84,0:53:24.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:53:25.97,0:53:27.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,別出聲
Dialogue: 0,0:53:32.01,0:53:33.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智 你的話有點過分了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.57,0:53:36.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是那傢伙說皮卡丘從我這裡逃跑了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:37.56,0:53:40.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那是因為小智先向魯卡利歐說了過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.77,0:53:45.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.78,0:53:57.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個沒吃過吧
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.93,0:54:04.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給 這是巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:54:05.13,0:54:05.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,巧克力
Dialogue: 0,0:54:06.91,0:54:11.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,生氣或心情不好的時候吃點甜食有好處
Dialogue: 0,0:54:22.72,0:54:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎樣
Dialogue: 0,0:54:42.16,0:54:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,睡覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.89,0:54:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是時候回到小鬼頭身邊去了
Dialogue: 0,0:55:10.92,0:55:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再多玩一會兒
Dialogue: 0,0:55:17.01,0:55:18.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,等到早上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.00,0:55:45.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:56:26.37,0:56:28.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐 怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.89,0:56:35.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是我…被封印的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.86,0:56:36.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,啊
Dialogue: 0,0:56:44.05,0:56:45.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:47.85,0:56:48.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:56:55.48,0:56:56.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,時間之花
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.26,0:57:06.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,亞倫大人
Dialogue: 0,0:58:11.85,0:58:13.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,住手 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:58:13.32,0:58:14.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這只是幻象
Dialogue: 0,0:58:31.27,0:58:32.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好可怕
Dialogue: 0,0:58:33.01,0:58:35.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是當年的戰場
Dialogue: 0,0:58:37.95,0:58:40.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐說的事情都是真的
Dialogue: 0,0:58:41.00,0:58:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看來是傳說有點錯誤呢
Dialogue: 0,0:58:44.12,0:58:48.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但是亞倫應該不是壞人吧
Dialogue: 0,0:58:48.42,0:58:50.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,難道說 將魯卡利歐封印
Dialogue: 0,0:58:51.04,0:58:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是為了不讓它捲進危險
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.97,0:58:57.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:59:08.99,0:59:09.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:59:12.01,0:59:15.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,完全沒有考慮你的心情 說了些過分的話
Dialogue: 0,0:59:19.71,0:59:20.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:59:23.68,0:59:24.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小智
Dialogue: 0,0:59:25.25,0:59:27.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你絕對不能放棄皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,0:59:30.07,0:59:30.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:59:37.38,0:59:38.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:42.37,0:59:44.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂 怎麼了 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.68,0:59:56.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷吉洛克
Dialogue: 0,0:59:58.08,0:59:59.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.13,1:00:04.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家 這邊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:17.13,1:00:17.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快走
Dialogue: 0,1:00:38.43,1:00:39.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:01:02.23,1:01:06.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那些孩子們 已經到達創世之樹了吧
Dialogue: 0,1:01:11.91,1:01:14.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,為什麼雷吉洛克會攻擊我們
Dialogue: 0,1:01:15.03,1:01:16.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它要我們不要靠近
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.84,1:01:17.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,警告
Dialogue: 0,1:01:19.88,1:01:23.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可能是創世之樹對侵入者的防衛吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:19.97,1:02:23.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是創世之樹的正下方了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:23.79,1:02:25.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,那皮卡丘呢
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.38,1:02:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就在上面
Dialogue: 0,1:02:26.31,1:02:27.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好 這就去 皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,1:02:27.97,1:02:29.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你知道路麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:30.00,1:02:31.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,總之向上就是了
Dialogue: 0,1:02:32.02,1:02:33.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,對吧 魯卡利歐
Dialogue: 0,1:02:33.18,1:02:33.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就算是吧
Dialogue: 0,1:02:34.11,1:02:34.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很好
Dialogue: 0,1:02:35.54,1:02:36.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,哎 小智
Dialogue: 0,1:02:37.39,1:02:38.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,呃 這是什麼
Dialogue: 0,1:02:38.40,1:02:39.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查模組
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.78,1:02:40.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,調查模組
Dialogue: 0,1:02:41.61,1:02:43.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,它能收集這裡的資料
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.56,1:02:48.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,班克斯
Dialogue: 0,1:02:48.47,1:02:50.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有工作了 快起來
Dialogue: 0,1:02:50.93,1:02:53.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已經就緒了 大小姐
Dialogue: 0,1:02:53.16,1:02:53.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看
Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.81,1:02:59.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創世之樹 數千年
Dialogue: 0,1:02:59.29,1:03:02.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 數萬年之間未受到外部的干涉
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.94,1:03:04.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,保護著小精靈們
Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.12,1:03:07.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭喜你的新發現
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.65,1:03:10.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,恭賀的話 留在揭開所有迷題之後吧
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.60,1:03:11.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:11.30,1:03:12.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,數據分析就拜託了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:12.80,1:03:13.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命
Dialogue: 0,1:03:16.28,1:03:17.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有點興奮了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.64,1:03:18.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在下也是
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.17,1:03:28.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我莫名地興奮起來了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:28.72,1:03:33.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡是稀有的小精靈到處遊蕩的寶山
Dialogue: 0,1:03:33.07,1:03:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不 是地下
Dialogue: 0,1:04:26.51,1:04:28.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這座岩石山是活著的
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.05,1:04:32.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,自然所創造的礦物生命體
Dialogue: 0,1:04:32.86,1:04:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,創世之樹吸收光能
Dialogue: 0,1:04:36.77,1:04:39.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,存活了幾萬年
Dialogue: 0,1:04:39.81,1:04:41.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,了不起的發現啊
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.62,1:04:44.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嗯 不過
Dialogue: 0,1:04:45.95,1:04:47.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還有迷題未被解開呢
Dialogue: 0,1:04:48.74,1:04:52.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,夢幻與創世之樹一定有什麼聯繫
Dialogue: 0,1:05:04.39,1:05:05.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這個是
Dialogue: 0,1:05:19.04,1:05:24.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喂～皮卡丘～ 我到這裡了～
Dialogue: 0,1:05:34.36,1:05:35.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,1:05:36.45,1:05:37.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,1:05:37.96,1:05:39.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在的話 回答一聲啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:40.26,1:05:41.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,1:05:50.48,1:05:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘
Dialogue: 0,1:05:53.34,1:05:56.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,皮卡丘 我這就來
Dialogue: 0,1:06:11.86,1:06:12.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,雷吉艾斯
Dialogue: 0,1:06:18.46,1:06:19.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不是敵人
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.07,1:06:21.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是來找同伴的
Dialogue: 0,1:06:26.78,1:06:29.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,似乎是無法說服的敵人 回去
