Dialogue: 0,1:06:38.45,1:06:39.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什麼嘛
Dialogue: 0,1:06:43.06,1:06:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家快跑
Dialogue: 0,1:06:44.51,1:06:45.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎麼了
