Dialogue: 0,1:06:55.98,1:06:56.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,找別的路
Dialogue: 0,1:07:03.84,1:07:04.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這裡
Dialogue: 0,1:07:18.88,1:07:20.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有人嗎
